[Name] Skim
[Summary] Skim is an input method platform based upon scim-lib optimized for KDE.
[Description] skim is an input method platform based upon scim-lib under *NIX 
systems (including GNU/Linux and FreeBSD) optimized for KDE. It provides a GUI
panel (named scim-panel-kde), a KConfig config module and setup dialogs for itself
and the libscim. It also has its own plugin system which supports on-demand 
loadable actions.
